---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Na Hua Kukui"
  description="Therapeutic and sacred bodywork for those standing at the edge of transformation. Rooted in Hawaiian lineage, offered one-on-one."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  {/* ── Section 1: Hero ── */}
  <section class="hero-section relative min-h-[90vh] md:min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    {/* Dark gradient overlay */}
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-black/70 via-bg-dark/60 to-accent/30 z-[1]" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    {/* Warm light radial accent */}
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[2]" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(201,162,76,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold text-gold tracking-wide mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">
        Na Hua Kukui
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-inverse/90 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 drop-shadow-md">
        Therapeutic and sacred bodywork for those standing at the edge of transformation. Rooted in Hawaiian lineage, offered one-on-one.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a session</a>
        <a href="#kukui" class="btn-secondary !border-white/40 !text-white hover:!bg-white/10">Learn more</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Scroll indicator */}
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce z-10" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold/60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ── Section 2: The Kukui ── */}
  <section id="kukui" class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-accent mb-6">The Kukui</h2>
          <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The kukui tree has been a source of light in Hawaiian life for generations. Its seeds were pressed for oil, burned to illuminate the night, and passed hand to hand as a symbol of guidance, lineage, and knowledge.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
            Na Hua Kukui &mdash; the seeds of light &mdash; carries this forward. The work offered here is a continuation of that lineage: bodywork as illumination, touch as transmission, each session a small kernel of something older than any one of us.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-accent/10 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-muted text-sm italic text-center px-6">
            Image: kukui tree, seeds, or hands-and-oil close-up
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ── Section 3: What's Offered ── */}
  <section class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-accent/10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-accent text-center mb-16">
        What's Offered
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {/* Card 1: Private Sessions */}
        <a href="/offerings" class="group block bg-white/60 border border-accent/10 rounded-sm p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-gold mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Private Sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Therapeutic and sacred bodywork, offered in person. Each session is shaped around what the body and the moment are asking for.
          </p>
        </a>

        {/* Card 2: Retreats with Jody */}
        <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group block bg-white/60 border border-accent/10 rounded-sm p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-gold mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Retreats with Jody</h3>
          <p class="text-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Deeper immersions led by Jody, teacher and carrier of this lineage. Held in places of stillness, opening space for longer transformation.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-xs text-gold font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">
            Visit Jody's site &rarr;
          </span>
        </a>

        {/* Card 3: The Lineage */}
        <a href="/about" class="group block bg-white/60 border border-accent/10 rounded-sm p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-gold mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">The Lineage</h3>
          <p class="text-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Every hand is trained by another. Learn about the teachers and tradition behind this work.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ── Section 4: Who This Is For ── */}
  <section class="bg-bg-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-inverse/90 leading-relaxed italic mb-10">
        These sessions are for people in good physical health who find themselves in transition &mdash; between chapters, careers, relationships, identities &mdash; and who want a holistic, embodied way through it. Not a fix. A forward movement.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a session</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
